<div id="enclosure">
  <h5 >Exam group max mark: 100, IA weightage: 50%, IA max marks: 50:</h5>
  <table id="pdf-table">
    <tr class="header">
      <td><%= "FA Criterion" %></td>
      <td><%= "Obtained Marks" %></td>
      <td><%= "Maximum Marks" %></td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <td><%= "A" %></td>
      <td><%= "24" %></td>
      <td><%= "30" %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><%= "B" %></td>
      <td><%= "8" %></td>
      <td><%= "10" %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><%= "C" %></td>
      <td><%= "3" %></td>
      <td><%= "5" %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><%= "D" %></td>
      <td><%= "4" %></td>
      <td><%= "5" %></td>
    </tr>

  </table>
  <h5 >1. Sum</h5>
  <div class="cgpas">
    <div class="batch-wise"><div class="title"><%= "Formula" %> &nbsp; : </div><div class="val themed_text">&nbsp; A+B+C+D </div> </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <%=image_tag('icse/sum_eg.png')%>
  </div>
  <h5 >2. Average</h5>
  <div class="cgpas">
    <div class="batch-wise"><div class="title"><%= "Formula" %> &nbsp; : </div><div class="val themed_text">&nbsp; avg(A,B,C,D,@conversion_factor) </div> </div>
  </div>
  <div class="info_text_regular">
    where A, B, C & D are the IA Indicators, @conversion_factor is the common mark to which the IA indicator marks are to be converted.
  </div>
  <div class="info_text_italic">
    @conversion_factor is only required if Total Marks Mode is used.
  </div>
  <div>
    <%=image_tag('icse/avg_eg.png')%>
  </div>
  <h5 >3. Best</h5>
  <div class="cgpas">
    <div class="batch-wise"><div class="title"><%= "Formula" %> &nbsp; : </div><div class="val themed_text">&nbsp; best(Count, A,B,C,D,@conversion_factor,:sum) </div> </div>
  </div>
  <div class="info_text_regular">
    where Count is the number of best marks to be taken, A,B,C,D are IA indicators, @conversion_factor is the common mark to which the IA indicator marks are converted and :sum indicates that the best marks taken should be summed up. If :sum is not given then the best marks are averaged by default.
  </div>
  <div class="info_text_italic">
    Both @conversion_factor and :sum are only required if Total Marks Mode is used.
  </div>
  <div>
    <%=image_tag('icse/best_eg.png')%>
  </div>
</div>